Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了营救被蓝染虏走的织姬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.39,0:01:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入虚圈的一护等人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突进破面们的老巢虚夜宫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶渡在与加廷拜恩战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.68,0:01:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体内的新能力得以觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在突然出现的十刃之一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺伊多拉的面前无力招架
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...切 看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很弱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶渡被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.81,0:02:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是发过誓的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好要活着回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.71,0:02:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会对那些不自量力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闯入这虚圈的家伙们的愚昧感到生气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 与阿洛尼洛对峙的露琪亚也陷入了危机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的能力叫做"喰虚"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞噬死亡之虚 将其能力和灵压为我所用的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙以志波海燕的身体返回虚圈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我整个给吞噬掉才得到的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个身体就是志波海燕的灵体本身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体内所有的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑中所有的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都完好地保留着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不过是将这些记忆和经历 读取出来再行动罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你见识见识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓十刃的刀剑解放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞噬一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"喰虚"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在恐惧着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再感到恐惧一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是至今为止 我所吞噬掉的所有虚的力量显现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要以为十刃的刀剣解放 和一般的破面差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的"喰虚"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能将所有吞噬掉的虚的能力 全部同时表现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今为止所吞噬的虚的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是三万三千六百五十
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将是超过三万的虚之军团
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一个人的对战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我...就只能到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为我杀害了海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才使得海燕大人的灵体落入虚的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为救自己而杀害了海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 让你难受了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了你...我的心...才得以留存
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.74,0:05:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人的身体从敌人手里夺过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少这一点是对海燕大人的救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在心里告诉自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎这一点...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经没有挥剑的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对海燕大人的灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已没有挥剑的...力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见...了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊 海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然打我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我怎么叫你 摇你 你都不回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一落枕怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,落枕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一边走路一边睡觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别发呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.45,0:07:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你丢下咯 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风吹到脸上的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林分出我前行的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草木的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪耀的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟的叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你到哪里去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.38,0:08:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一棵棵的树木
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不安 兴奋和温暖交织在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼之欲出的这份情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:39.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是西流魂街三区北端的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲤伏山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次带我修行的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是新入队员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是副队长志波海燕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这算什么招呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边可是副队长在跟你报名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也应该自报家门 并请我多多指教才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字叫什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫朽木...露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.92,0:09:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK了 露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平凡的招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平凡的怒声
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平凡的下级与上级的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十三番队欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.59,0:09:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们队上的队长身体不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上都是我在管理啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你也可以偶尔叫错 称我为海燕队长哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这种平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却正是我所追求的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不够呢 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.54,0:10:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟儿飞过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这一瞬间我被鸟分散了注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二击就被海燕大人从左下方攻入
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切我都记得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是非常专注的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是想吃饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.13,0:10:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个超级自我中心的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...不是的啦 海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦 别在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海...海燕大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱扔出了鞘的刀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都会肚子饿的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.22,0:11:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用不着这么害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时的我 心中有所不安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入队仪式顺利完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几席啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭我的能力还无法...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一入队马上就成为席官...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本就缺乏剑术的天赋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知罪梦之壁 仅立其上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破道之三十三 苍火坠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在灵术院时鬼道的成绩还算不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在护廷队中也只属一般
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的可以呆在护廷十三队中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟为了什么而呆在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟为了什么而在这里的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情不是明摆着的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了守护而战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要守护什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.03,0:12:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么...你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啦 那个啦 很多东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来实在是很模糊不清的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有其它更明确一些的回答吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明确的回答啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木 你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有听过我们队长的一贯主张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗分为两种
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护生命的战斗和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守卫尊严的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是浮竹队长的一贯主张
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得无论哪种战斗 最终都是在守护相同的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相同的东西...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:01.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃... 好酸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我可是很认真地在说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我问你啊 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得"心"在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这...这个嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就是在这... 附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得 心啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你接触的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心就在我们之间生成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心不在身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,思索什么的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想念谁的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心就在那里生成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果世界上只有自己孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:15:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就不存在什么心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人确实是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么好烦恼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你衷心希望能呆在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你的心就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心在这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这就是你呆在这里的理由了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将来你战斗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事绝对不能做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独自死去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的身体就是魂魄本身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死后身体自然会化作尘土
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为包围尸魂界的灵子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时心会去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心要交给同伴保管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给同伴...保管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将心交给同伴保管的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心就会在那个人体内继续生存
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你绝对不能独自死去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心要交给同伴保管
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有意识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命真大 不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说是可怜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.37,0:17:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你怎样苟延残喘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也无法改变你不能斩杀我的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还留有握刀柄的力气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道你想起了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用折断的刀战斗的蠢事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太碍眼了 放下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心的所在之处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你身体里确实是海燕大人的灵体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 海燕大人并不在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海燕大人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经交给我保管了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十刃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦 好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我 蓝染大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝染大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说过的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.87,0:19:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我跟着你 就会从一切痛苦中解放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦 好痛苦 好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要 我不要 我不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对...不会...认同的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别死啊 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你千万不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解什么是孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为被捕者的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解什么是喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴前来搭救时的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那些同伴受伤被打倒时的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.54,0:21:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.50,0:21:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.40,0:21:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在... 就去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺伊多拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.73,0:23:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前几天您用手指 指着地面是在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是用这种方法 寻找整个虚夜宫中的灵压
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.12,0:23:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情也可以做得到的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.71,0:23:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也试试
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走 泰斯拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.67,0:23:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.95,0:23:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们别无视我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神图鉴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有钱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次的预算已经用得差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.03,0:23:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都太乱花钱了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.60,0:23:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长您用得最多了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 为了快速凑集经费
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拍些名人的生活照来卖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.73,0:23:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说在现世搞偷拍的狗仔师都赚了大钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.09,0:24:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标是护廷十三队的明星们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.82,0:24:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解散
